code: import React from"react";export default function Button(props){var className=["button"];if(props.isPrimary)className.push("button-primary");if(props.isWideMobile)className.push("button-wide-mobile");if(props.isSmall)className.push("button-sm");if(props.isBlock)className.push("button-block");return React.createElement("button",{className:className.join(" ")},props.children);}
